處3年以上10年以下有期徒刑，得併科2百萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c501%2c20220816%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,交易,501,20220816,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交易","JNO":"501","JDATE":"20220816","JTITLE":"公共危險"}